text: Imran Uzzaman (born 4 November 1994) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his List A debut for Prime Doleshwar Sporting Club in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 27 March 2019. He made his first-class debut for Khulna Division in the 2019–20 National Cricket League on 10 October 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Khulna Division cricketers Category:Prime Doleshwar Sporting Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
